A fragrance designed as a unisex offering, Mukhallat Shams brings together Floral Woody elements with the use of Rose and Sandalwood. A hearty dose of Dahn Al Oudh reminds the wearer of the Al Shams heritage, providing richness to the fragrance with Musk providing warmth, longevity and radiance to the wearer. It is a fragrance that is aimed at confident and grounded individuals who love oriental fragrances that depict their tastes strongly.

Oud Lavender is composed of premium Oud, Lavender and highly concentrated in Agarwood Oil, created to transport you to a world of unique and intense pleasure.
This unisex, luxurious romantic perfume is ideal for a romantic evening, official and social engagements. Its irresistible scent will leave everyone around you wanting more.
OUD LAVENDER composition:
Top notes: Citrus
Middle notes: Floral
Base notes: Woody
